definitions.definition: A former continent in Earth . A proposed ancient continent that would later merge together with the continents of Vaalbara and Sclavia to form the supercontinent Kenorland .
Synonym of Superior Craton , a sub- craton forming part of the Canadian Shield , the continental core of North America
